(b) the Municipal Treasurer and Municipal Accountant to maintain PC, PPELC, and Real Property Card for easy reconciliation of the accounts;

(c) instruct the Municipal Accountant to ensure that all payments are adequately and properly supported by required documents prior to payment; and 

(d) instruct the Municipal Budget Officer and the Municipal Accountant to correct  the misclassification of the PPE accounts in the Budget and the Accounting records.

